name: Storytime
description: Mixed media art journal pages made in an upcycled modular planner, 9" x 7", 5451 x 4104 px, acrylic paint, vintage/found paper, ink. Cento and title composed with words found in Just For Fun, a California State Textbook published in 1954 and Jim and Judy, a school primer published by The Macmillan Company in 1939.
